name: Spalted Ash Telecaster type Electric Guitar
description:
One piece, solid body, spalted Swamp Ash.
Birds eye Maple kneck.
Walnut Fingerboard.
Inlaid abolone and mother of pearl, Ivy and Lilly design on the headstock.
Bare Knuckle Blackguard single coil pick ups with a series /parallel switching option at the the selector switch.  Adds a humbucker type tone to the tonal options.
All Gotoh hardware, bridge and tuners.

name: Steel String Acoustic Guitar (Sitka, Rosewood, Ziricote)
description:
Currently in progress...

Sitka top, Rosewood back and sides, Mahogany neck, Ziricote fingerboard and bridge.
Ebony headstock veneer inlaid Black Tahiti mother-of-pearl.
645mm Scale length, 14 fret join.
Under saddle pick up.
Gotoh tuners.
Hand tuned top and back.
Black Tahiti Mother of Pearl sound hole decoration.

name: 5 Metre Guitar Cable - Neutrik and Klotz
description:
5 Metre Klotz AC106SW Instrument Cable

 **I can make up any length or connector type that you require, just contact me**

1 Core 6mm constructed with a PVC jacket, double shielded with a copper core. 

Colour: Black 


1 x Neutrik ‘Silent’ Connector

Gold plated Neutrik 'Silent' plugs automatically mutes (shorts) an instrument cable to avoid pops and squeals when changing the instrument under load. 

The integrated gold contact reed switch is activated by a spring-loaded magnetic sleeve that un-shorts the contacts only when the jack is fully mated. 

The switch is hermetically sealed, and is rated for at least 10,000 mating cycles.  Diecast shell, Neutrik unique chuck-type strain relief with PU-sleeve for optimal cable protection.

 

1 x Neutrik Connector

Professional, high standard connector as above without the

silent’ jacket.

 

Hand built by guitar maker Owen Davies using Silver Solder.
